      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The exterior remains clean and presentable, showing only minor signs of regular road use such as small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin is well-kept and comfortable, with all features and controls functioning as expected. It offers a smooth driving experience, making it a great choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for, reliable vehicle.",
