    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
