      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD in flawless condition. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, showing exceptional compression across all faces. The chassis retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution remains undisturbed. Completely stock with no aftermarket modifications, the vacuum lines have been meticulously maintained to prevent heat-soak issues. Numbers-matching, original paint with zero oxidation, and a pristine interior make this a definitive collector-grade investment for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
