      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary vehicle, preserved in an impeccable state that transcends the standard pre-owned market. This automobile exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a meticulously maintained interior that reflects a history of absolute care. Every component has been vetted to ensure it meets the highest standards of automotive excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to secure a vehicle of unrivaled caliber and pristine condition. We invite you to schedule a private viewing to appreciate this masterpiece of engineering and preservation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
